    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Define the snippet.</p><figure class="highlight json"><figcaption><span>updated.code-snippets</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;Hexo front-matter updated&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;scope&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;yaml&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Insert the updated time for hexo&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;prefix&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;hexo-fm-up&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;body&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="string">&quot;updated: $CURRENT_YEAR-$CURRENT_MONTH-$CURRENT_DATE $CURRENT_HOUR:$CURRENT_MINUTE:$CURRENT_SECOND&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        ]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><p>Set tab completion to <code>onlySnippets</code>.<br><img src="tab-completion.png" alt="tab completion"></p><p>For more information, check <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9jb2RlLnZpc3VhbHN0dWRpby5jb20vZG9jcy9lZGl0b3IvdXNlcmRlZmluZWRzbmlwcGV0cyNfY3JlYXRlLXlvdXItb3duLXNuaXBwZXRz">VSCode Doc<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></p><p>Create snippets of the project.<br><img src="config-snippet.gif" alt="config snippet"></p><p>Test it.<br><img src="snippet.gif" alt="snippet sample"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Define the snippet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight json&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;span&gt;updated.code-snippets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Hexo front-matter updated&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &amp;#123;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;scope&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;yaml&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;description&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Insert the updated time for hexo&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;prefix&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;hexo-fm-up&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;attr&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;body&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;: [&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;updated: $CURRENT_YEAR-$CURRENT_MONTH-$CURRENT_DATE $CURRENT_HOUR:$CURRENT_MINUTE:$CURRENT_SECOND&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;        ]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;    &amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&amp;#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
