  <entry>
    <title>Systemd Service Sample: Hexo Server</title>
    <link href="https://weiliwlai.github.io/blog/systemd-service-sample-hexo-server/"/>
    <id>https://weiliwlai.github.io/blog/systemd-service-sample-hexo-server/</id>
    <published>2020-10-22T08:13:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-22T16:58:34.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Assume that Hexo is already installed, check <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv">Hexo doc<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span> for more information.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/systemd/system/hexo-server.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption><span>hexo-server.service</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[Unit]</span><br><span class="line">Description=Hexo Server</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Service]</span><br><span class="line">Type=simple</span><br><span class="line">User=weili</span><br><span class="line">WorkingDirectory=/home/weili/hexo-blog</span><br><span class="line">ExecStart=hexo server -s -p 8080</span><br><span class="line">Restart=always</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[Install]</span><br><span class="line">WantedBy=multi-user.target</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Enable, reload and start service.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> hexo-server.service</span><br><span class="line">sudo service hexo-server start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Check the status.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo service hexo-server status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Assume that Hexo is already installed, check &lt;span class=&quot;exturl&quot; data-url=&quot;aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv&quot;&gt;Hexo doc&lt;i class=&quot;fa fa-external-link-alt&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight bash&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo vim /etc/systemd/system/hexo-server.service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
